{"tid":785371,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"以為奪歐洲賽女子5000米銀牌盡情慶祝　點知仲有一個圈","createTime":"2018-08-19T07:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T11:35:40.000Z","uid":19889,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f20f55c8107f4983317db25944c10f00910344ae","tid":785371,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"在周日（8月12日）舉行的歐洲田徑錦標賽女子5000米決賽，來到最後階段，冠軍是荷蘭選手施芬哈辛（Sifan Hassan）及以色列選手莎比德之爭，前者稍為領先。當代表最後一圈的鐘聲響起，施芬哈辛繼續領放，但莎比德竟然在慶祝！她以為自己贏了銀牌！大概4秒後，她才回神，猛然發現比賽尚有一圈，她只是跑了4600米！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1746375/org/44b3903c0ca8bf8fecacada79a2e48e1.jpg/Y7WZSEolKqQfBcrUM_YZIRwvW6DxL_Ad3U8m0N1PJtA?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1746375%2Forg%2F44b3903c0ca8bf8fecacada79a2e48e1.jpg%2FY7WZSEolKqQfBcrUM_YZIRwvW6DxL_Ad3U8m0N1PJtA%3Fv%3Dw1760&h=99211e2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1746364/org/40ed54c88cb217c5127625f484ed28fd.jpg/UbHSTZ7h22L_uZ4NPR7Li9jsZp45T1zk5H5W3uR-Vt4?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1746364%2Forg%2F40ed54c88cb217c5127625f484ed28fd.jpg%2FUbHSTZ7h22L_uZ4NPR7Li9jsZp45T1zk5H5W3uR-Vt4%3Fv%3Dw1760&h=2994fa5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1746375/org/44b3903c0ca8bf8fecacada79a2e48e1.jpg/Y7WZSEolKqQfBcrUM_YZIRwvW6DxL_Ad3U8m0N1PJtA?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1746375%2Forg%2F44b3903c0ca8bf8fecacada79a2e48e1.jpg%2FY7WZSEolKqQfBcrUM_YZIRwvW6DxL_Ad3U8m0N1PJtA%3Fv%3Dw1760&h=99211e2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1746381/org/a48769c2f66ffedc4918b774ce0b4bfd.jpg/siZCsNyqFPUneJgICcpnSBGEEFHmDAkvyLgByMi4Acg?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1746381%2Forg